  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9300362d8f2051497661661a7b184e7a.poster.avif?t=1692783729\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9300362d8f2051497661661a7b184e7a.webm?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9300362d8f2051497661661a7b184e7a.mp4?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>RUSA Odyssey is a third-person exploration game set in the post-apocalypse world. Play as a lone deer and traverse the unknown mysterious world. Find a way to The End and discover the story along the way.<br><br>You play as a deer, explore the world, and find your way to The End.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>If you like Journey, you might like this game too.<br></li><li>Featuring a beautiful soundtrack by SAVFX & ALEKSEY CHISTILIN<br></li><li>A short game with some platforming and light puzzles.</li></ul><br>Note: <br>A game inspired by Journey, The Last of Us, The First Tree, Inside & Movie; The Maze Runner.<br>A game by a solo dev.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9d047941542ae428e914e39b89e196d5.poster.avif?t=1692783729\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9d047941542ae428e914e39b89e196d5.webm?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9d047941542ae428e914e39b89e196d5.mp4?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9300362d8f2051497661661a7b184e7a.poster.avif?t=1692783729\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9300362d8f2051497661661a7b184e7a.webm?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9300362d8f2051497661661a7b184e7a.mp4?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>RUSA Odyssey is a third-person exploration game set in the post-apocalypse world. Play as a lone deer and traverse the unknown mysterious world. Find a way to The End and discover the story along the way.<br><br>You play as a deer, explore the world, and find your way to The End.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>If you like Journey, you might like this game too.<br></li><li>Featuring a beautiful soundtrack by SAVFX & ALEKSEY CHISTILIN<br></li><li>A short game with some platforming and light puzzles.</li></ul><br>Note: <br>A game inspired by Journey, The Last of Us, The First Tree, Inside & Movie; The Maze Runner.<br>A game by a solo dev.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9d047941542ae428e914e39b89e196d5.poster.avif?t=1692783729\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9d047941542ae428e914e39b89e196d5.webm?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538890/extras/9d047941542ae428e914e39b89e196d5.mp4?t=1692783729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
